{"tid":1171991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"朗迷咁開心做咩？你唔講我仲以為c朗拿度攞咗意大利盃添。","createTime":"2019-05-26T06:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T09:02:00.000Z","uid":43785,"like":20,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"62c73429274a87eb0dc933482580fbff9283a66f","tid":1171991,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:16:02.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母c朗拿度，攞唔撚到意大利盃真係好柒。<br />\n<br />\nc朗拿度柒撚咗架啦，班球迷好心就唔好撲出嚟講嘢啦。<br />\n屌你老母你個鬥心求王，但帶唔起隊波。<br />\n你嚟咗意甲，搞到冇意大利杯呀傻閪。<br />\n<br />\nc朗拿度攞唔到意大利盃七撚咗就收聲啦。 你地有乜撚嘢資格笑呀。<br />\n傻閪朗迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e676d6ffe12353666aff08fccefc45f6a2e46800","tid":1171991,"uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:19:29.000Z","msg":"c朗拿度講到自己幾勁幾勁<br />\n連意大利嗰杯都攞唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日輸波，因為美斯班隊友廢，同教練排怪陣<br />\n<br />\n搞到美斯冇咗個杯，根本就唔係球王美斯嘅問題， C朗拿度球迷講到好似係美斯好大責任咁樣，食撚屎啦你哋。<br />\n美斯已經有入波㗎喇，隊友失波關佢屁事？<br />\n教練用怪陣又關美斯佢事？<br />\n<br />\n醒少少啦c朗拿度球迷"},{"pid":"fa2b069127080bb57c21b860b3bad863b06eea03","tid":1171991,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:20:38.000Z","msg":"意大利盃8強<br />\n比阿特蘭大炒3:0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n意大利盃零入球"},{"pid":"af96a6e1c112182eb79557ac43d699becce789f3","tid":1171991,"uid":92972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:21:29.000Z","msg":"你咁認真做咩 輸就輸啦 咁多野講"},{"pid":"e18e1e05b9cbdce5c37183757f98677943c410c5","tid":1171991,"uid":141543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"鳩硬蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"